reviewText: Cloud Computing Law Specialization course is beyond magnificent for young scholars and researchers interested in data security. It offers a wide range of topics in the most simple terms and relatable examples. You wouldn't want to stop reading this course until you are done. It is definitely worth all the stars!

I audited the course and found it most helpful and I learned a lot, a lot of stuff that I was missing on cloud computing law. In fact, it is an easy 5 star as it was just at the right level for me. Thank you QMUL!
